      <para>This document is the official user manual to OmegaT, the free
      Computer-Assisted Translation tool.</para>

	  <para>OmegaT's main purpose is to help you create a good translation the
	  fastest possible by giving you access to your translation ressources in
	  the most reliable way possible.</para>

